            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E6%93%A4%E9%BC%BB%E6%B6%95%E6%88%96%E8%87%B4%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%B5%E9%BC%93%E8%86%9C%E7%A9%BF%E5%AD%94%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E6%93%A4%E9%BC%BB%E6%B6%95%E6%88%96%E8%87%B4%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%B5%E9%BC%93%E8%86%9C%E7%A9%BF%E5%AD%94%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#错误擤鼻涕或致耳朵鼓膜穿孔#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】人体内耳毛细胞的纤毛会随声波“一起摇摆”。长期在噪声环境中，毛细胞将有“摇”不动的一天。当纤毛损坏达到一定规模，就会产生听力损害。日常生活中，错误的擤鼻涕方式可能造成鼓膜穿孔，常用硬物掏耳朵容易损伤耳道皮肤。今天爱耳日，一起爱护耳朵！ <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4875120389587028" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hbmczb4gwyj61n20x8kjl02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/o7VqrC7blx083zwVwjTW01041200Bvmy0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1677921695&amp;ssig=YsoPInrghW&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/NVKbhU2llx083zwVmrJS01041200iGxg0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1677921695&amp;ssig=gbywtrezEP&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/Xf7gxFI6lx083zwUW9O801041200bRGc0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1677921695&amp;ssig=fk%2FjcanMS1&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4875120389587028&amp;luicode=10000011&a